\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the eventual victors\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stroke Matt Edge was clearly flailing, his oar only just dipping in the water, but Cambridge's lead proved too big an ask for Oxford as Edge's crew rallied around their tiring teammate to claim another victory.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"score\": 0.9991500004006626, \"rank\": 0.0008507226338269921, \"text\": \"Edge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\"}, {\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 0.9979823066238225, \"rank\": 0.002021772693745469, \"text\": \"Cambridge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 2350, \"end\": 2356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\", \"score\": 0.9988132144174013, \"rank\": 0.0011881957158835195, \"text\": \"Oxford\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\"}, {\"begin\": 2360, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"score\": 0.9991500004006626, \"rank\": 0.0008507226338269921, \"text\": \"Edge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his oar\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"too big an ask\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"their tiring teammate\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"another victory\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bow and president Sebastien Benzecry paid tribute to Edge's effort after the race, stating: \\\"Credit to Matt, to go that deep, a lot of that margin was down to him.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2489, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"score\": 0.9991500004006626, \"rank\": 0.0008507226338269921, \"text\": \"Edge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Edge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bow\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"president Sebastien Benzecry\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"Credit\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"that margin\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was putting down a dynamic rhythm, it takes a lot out of you in the stroke seat.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dynamic rhythm\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"the stroke seat\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So proud of him, an amazing race.\\\"\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oxford's Leonard Jenkins revealed that the men's team fell ill earlier in the day due to theE colistrain.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2722, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\", \"score\": 0.998813