, \"to\": 3028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I could not be prouder of the guys.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prouder\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a great battle.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great battle\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a shame the result does not suit that, Cambridge showed their class and did to us what we wanted to do for them.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 0.9979823066238225, \"rank\": 0.002021772693745469, \"text\": \"Cambridge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shame\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3132}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"their class\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3192}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe experience [was the difference]?\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maybe experience\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not sure.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not expect it to be such a big difference.\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a big difference\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will also say, it's in no way to take away from Cambridge.\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 0.9979823066238225, \"rank\": 0.002021772693745469, \"text\": \"Cambridge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had a few guys go down pretty badly with theE colistrain.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few guys\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"theE colistrain\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This morning, I was throwing up and I really wasn't sure there was a chance for me to be in the boat.\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I kept that quiet, that's on my shoulders.\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my shoulders\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not sure if that was the right choice because I did not feel like I had much to give.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right choice\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it would have been taking one of the top guys out of [reserve boat] Isis and ruining their chances.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3780, \"end\": 3784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Isis\", \"score\": 0.6897234199231467, \"rank\": 0.44985652380961294, \"text\": \"Isis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Isis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Isis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top guys\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3757}, {\"ngram\": \"[reserve boat\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3778}, {\"ngram\": \"their chances\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like we needed to give them a fair fight.\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fair fight\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would have been ideal to not have so much poo in the water.\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much poo\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not to take away from Cambridge, I do not know if we would have had a chance to beat them even if we were all on form.\\\"\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3955, \"end\": 3964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 0.9979823066238225, \"rank\": 0.002021772693745469, \"text\": \"Cambridge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4105, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3849020065440908e-14, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\":